{"tid":2268162,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"魔靈召喚香港選手挺入世界總決賽!!!!!","createTime":"2020-11-02T14:47:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T14:59:19.000Z","uid":321228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5fbc957dc2652551c58572f664ef6ef47118db99","tid":2268162,"uid":321228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T14:47:29.000Z","msg":"Com2uS 旗下《魔靈召喚》所舉辦的世界競技場全球最強冠軍賽（以下簡稱 SWC），今年已邁入第 4 屆，而 SWC 也已經成為全球召喚師每年所期待的最大盛典，今年賽事總獎金更高達 21 萬美金（約 630 萬台幣）。於 11 月 1 日所舉行的亞洲區決賽中，香港選手「醉愛鍾少（MR.CHUNG）」一路過關斬將贏得冠軍，台灣選手「GAIA」也順利拿到第三名，一同挺進 11 月 21 日的世界總決賽。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.gamer.com.tw/gnn/detail.php?sn=205697\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.gamer.com.tw%2Fgnn%2Fdetail.php%3Fsn%3D205697&d=tGWxp70K68wBh01xS7f0EhR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=44a87772\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.gamer.com.tw/gnn/detail.php?sn=205697</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鍾少加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccafe7d876b0d28133bf01ee1a7d42c7a6c6466f","tid":2268162,"uid":98473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T14:59:19.000Z","msg":"拎左champ之後<br />\n平時笑電莖既人就會大叫香港之光<br />\nproud of you<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}